        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
                 throws java.io.IOException
        Analyzes the input texts.

        Usage: SudachiCommandLine [-r file] [-m A|B|C] [-o file] [-d] [file ...]

        The following are the options.

        -r file
        the settings file in JSON format
        -m {A|B|C}
        the mode of splitting
        -o file
        the output file
        -a
        print all of the fields
        -d
        print the debug informations
        -h
        show the usage

        If the output file is not specified, this tool writes the output to the standard output.

        The file operands are processed in command-line order. If file is absent, this tool reads from the starndard input.

        This tool processes a line as a sentence.

        パラメータ:
        args - the options and the input filenames
        例外:
        java.io.IOException - if IO is failed
